codBlock.title: Code of Conduct
codBlock.summary: GDG Cloud Melbourne is dedicated to providing a harassment-free DevFest experience for everyone regardless of gender, gender identity and expression, sexual orientation, disability, physical appearance, body size, race, age or religion. We do not tolerate harassment of DevFest participants in any form. Sexual language and imagery is not appropriate for any DevFest venue, including talks. DevFest participants violating these rules may be sanctioned or expelled from the DevFest without a refund at the discretion of the DevFest organizers.
